        <li>Ensure workloads, content, and integrations are authorized and lawful.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Article 5. Fees and payment</h2>
      <p>
        Fees, invoicing frequency, and payment terms are specified in commercial ordering documents or the applicable
        subscription agreement.
